            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>Hello, I'm Dr. Nur Aycicek, an Educational Program Specialist with over 14 years of experience in higher and adult education. I specialize in instructional design, e-learning, and hybrid modules. I hold a Ph.D. in Instructional Design and Technologies from Sheffield University and an MA in International Education from Leicester University. I am proficient in both German and English and have worked at prestigious institutions like NATO Centre of Excellence for Stability Policing and Abdullah Gul University.</p>
